{"_id":"5i89q5azposMAFyW","name":"Hazirawn (Greatsword)","permission":{"default":0,"iUkeYDgfDBka4Q8T":3},"type":"weapon","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">A sentient (neutral evil) greatsword,&nbsp;</span><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">Hazirawn&nbsp;</em><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">is capable of speech in Common and Netherese. Even if you aren&rsquo;t attuned to the sword, you gain a +1 bonus on attack rolls and damage rolls made with this weapon. If you are attuned to&nbsp;</span><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">Hazirawn</em><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">, you deal an extra 1d6 necrotic damage when you hit with the weapon.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\" /><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Increased Potency.&nbsp;</strong></em><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">While you are attuned to this weapon, its bonus on attack rolls and damage rolls increases to +2, and a hit deals an extra 2d6 necrotic damage (instead of 1d6).</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\" /><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Spells.&nbsp;</strong>Hazirawn&nbsp;</em><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">has 4 charges to cast spells. As long as the sword is attuned to you and you are holding it in your hand, you can cast&nbsp;</span><a class=\"entity-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\" draggable=\"true\" data-pack=\"dnd5e.spells\" data-id=\"ghXTfe7sgCbgf1Q8\">&nbsp;Detect Magic</a><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</em><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">(1 charge),&nbsp;</span><a class=\"entity-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\" draggable=\"true\" data-pack=\"dnd5e.spells\" data-id=\"Mzh95utKDPIrjiH8\">&nbsp;Detect Evil and Good</a><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</em><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">(1 charge), or&nbsp;</span><a class=\"entity-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\" draggable=\"true\" data-pack=\"dnd5e.spells\" data-id=\"ppWAAEul0QHtm4er\">&nbsp;Detect Thoughts</a><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</em><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">(2 charges). Each night at midnight, Hazirawn regains 1d4 expended charges.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\" /><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Wounding.&nbsp;</strong></em><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">While you are attuned to the weapon, any creature that you hit with&nbsp;</span><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">Hazirawn&nbsp;</em><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">can&rsquo;t regain hit points for 1 minute. The target can make a DC 15 Constitution saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending this effect early on a success.</span></p>\n<p><em><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">Note: Ithe weapon is set to work as if you were already attuned. If you use it while not attuned, reduce the Necrotic damage and Attack and Damage bonus accordingly.</span></em></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Hoard of the Dragon Queen","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attuned":false,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":2,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d6 + @mod + 2","slashing"],["2d6","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":15,"scaling":"flat"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","properties":{"amm":false,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"hvy":true,"lgt":false,"lod":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"two":true,"ver":false},"proficient":true},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.GbKQbjFLbfGOFYQg"}},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/violet_04.jpg","effects":[]}
